lyVacButton1\" src=\"http://img03.zhaopin.cn/2012/other/search/images/apply_btn.png\" style=\"border: none; cursor: pointer; \" /></dd>\r\n	<dd class=\"clearfix\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; float: none; line-height: 28px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); width: 771px; height: 0px; font-size: 0px; overflow: hidden; \">\r\n		&nbsp;</dd>\r\n</dl>\r\n<h2 class=\"company-headline\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 35px; height: 35px; background-color: rgb(237, 246, 255); \">职位描述</h2>\r\n<div class=\"company-introduction\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 10px; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); line-height: 24px; \">\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 12px; min-height: 16px; \">\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">主要负责游戏中角色三维动画的制作。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">任职要求：</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">1、熟练使用maya或max等三维软件，尤其是相应动画模块的相关操作。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">&nbsp;2、对动画有较深刻的理解和认识，节奏和pose把握到位，并有自己独特的想法和见解！</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">&nbsp;3、具备良好的团队合作意识，工作态度严谨，有责任心。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">&nbsp;4、有较强的自我学习提高意识，善于同团队成员相互沟通，共同提高。</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">同时满足以下条件之一会优先考虑：</div>\r\n<div style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); min-height: 16px; \">&nbsp;1、有一年或以上的三维机械动画制作经验。</div>\r\n<div sty