弹追踪、导弹加速和巡航、炮弹受重力和风力的影响等等。</span></p>\r\n	<h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \">模拟驾驶仿真实验室（虚拟实验室）</h2>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">所谓模拟，就是用一个系统模仿另一个系统的过程。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">模拟驾驶仿真系统是基于虚拟现实</span>仿真技术开发的半实物仿真系统，总的来说，分两类：<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">1</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">）一种是驾驶模拟</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">.2</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">）另外一种是操作模拟。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">驾驶模拟包括各种交通工具（如车辆、飞行器、船等）、特殊工业机械（如起重机、吊车等）、战斗机械（如战机、坦克、装甲车等）的驾驶操作的模拟。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">操作模拟包括各种机械设备的操作模拟（如数控机床、机电设备等）</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://www.3dvr-cn.com/media/upload/image/2012/11/16/22_3.jpg\" style=\"margin: 5px 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; max-width: 680px; \" /></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">特点：</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">经济性、安全性、逼真性。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">使用模拟驾驶仿真系统，让我们的实验研究和实操训练摆脱了时间、空间、天气、环境、资金等因素的影响。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \">&nbsp;</p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">技术服务：</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">朗途科技专注于虚拟现实技术应用，长期订做各种模拟驾驶仿真系统。目前有汽车、飞行器、航海、火炮、工具车辆等的模拟驾驶仿真系统。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">公司技术力量雄厚，长期为部队、博物馆、科技馆、培训机构、企业、游戏场所等开发模拟驾驶系统，经验丰富，技术全面，工作效率高。</span></p>\r\n	<p align=\"LEFT\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; width: 680px; word-wrap: break-word; text-indent: 0.85cm; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(246, 244, 245); \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; font: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; \">我们掌握有全套模拟驾驶仿真技术：视景仿真系统、动力学仿真模拟系统、数据库、考核评分系统、分布式交互仿真系统、仿真控制系统、互动力学反应系统。</span></p>\r\n	</td>\r\n	</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n','0','','0','10000','','0','','0','1','|0');
